FAQs
What is Rydas?

Rydas is a mobility investment company providing motorcycles on a lease-to-own basis, enabling individuals onboard in high-demand food and grocery delivery services and generate income above minimum wage
Where is Rydas available?
We are currently available in ibadan. We are working on expanding to your city
Am i eligible to be a Ryda?
Anyone with a valid drivers license, police report, 2 guarantors and a witness is eligible to be a Ryda
Do i need to pay a deposit?
No you’re not required to pay a deposit.
Who is responsible for maintenance and insurance?
We are solely responsible for all routine maintenance and insurance as we aim to take the burden off you.
Do i need a smartphone?
Yes, you’ll need a smart phone to work with the integrated delivery services. In fact, we also provide a smartphone contract, if interested.
